757
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:35,340
♪Dust of the night
shields the future from decay♪

758
00:40:35,340 --> 00:40:36,660
I want to toast you two.

759
00:40:37,860 --> 00:40:39,180
If it weren't for you,

760
00:40:39,260 --> 00:40:40,860
this case wouldn't have been resolved
so quickly.

761
00:40:41,300 --> 00:40:42,460
We owe Shaozhong a huge thank you.

762
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:44,820
He stepped up and took a risk,

763
00:40:44,820 --> 00:40:46,900
giving us the crucial time
we needed to turn everything around.

764
00:40:48,980 --> 00:40:49,980
A toast to Shaozhong.

765
00:40:50,700 --> 00:40:51,220
Here.

766
00:40:51,340 --> 00:40:51,940
Cheers.

767
00:40:59,500 --> 00:41:00,180
Where's Shaohua?

768
00:41:06,660 --> 00:41:07,980
I knew I'd find you here.

769
00:41:16,660 --> 00:41:17,500
What's wrong?

770
00:41:20,260 --> 00:41:21,260
You can finally let go

771
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,660
of everything from the past.

772
00:41:24,380 --> 00:41:25,180
Doesn't that make you happy?

773
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:27,460
Yes,

774
00:41:28,700 --> 00:41:29,540
revenge has been taken

775
00:41:32,540 --> 00:41:33,660
and the case is closed.

776
00:41:36,260 --> 00:41:38,180
But I still feel a sense of loss...

777
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:43,580
for all that I've lost.

778
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:51,940
What's lost is lost.

779
00:41:53,100 --> 00:41:54,140
So let's move on

780
00:41:54,940 --> 00:41:55,780
and focus on the present.

781
00:41:59,260 --> 00:42:00,020
What

782
00:42:00,700 --> 00:42:02,340
do we have now?

783
00:42:07,700 --> 00:42:08,500
Now,

784
00:42:09,940 --> 00:42:10,740
we have money,

785
00:42:12,860 --> 00:42:13,940
your career,

786
00:42:14,500 --> 00:42:15,260
my restaurant,

787
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:17,340
and

788
00:42:18,220 --> 00:42:19,060
someone who's in love with you.

789
00:42:22,740 --> 00:42:23,340
You love me?

790
00:42:27,020 --> 00:42:28,300
Have you not noticed

791
00:42:29,420 --> 00:42:30,580
that there's someone

792
00:42:31,300 --> 00:42:32,620
