793
00:42:34,820 --> 00:42:35,540
all this time?

794
00:42:44,060 --> 00:42:44,700
Him?

795
00:42:48,460 --> 00:42:50,260
Bai.

796
00:42:50,460 --> 00:42:51,260
Coming.

797
00:42:53,580 --> 00:42:54,580
Just think about it.

